<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
     <h4>Support Request</h4>
    <p>
      This is to inform you that you have a support Request .
      Details are given below.<br><br>
      <b>1. Support Request Raise By</b> - <%= @issue_request.employee.try(:manual_employee_code) %> <%= @issue_request.employee.try(:first_name) %> <%= @issue_request.employee.try(:middle_name) %> <%= @issue_request.employee.try(:last_name) %><br><br>

      <b>2. Extension Line No. 1 - <%= @issue_request.employee.try(:contact_no) %></b>

      <b>3. Department - <%= @issue_request.employee.try(:department).try(:name) %></b>

      <b>4. Official Email - <%= @issue_request.employee.try(:email) %></b>

      <b>5. Support Type</b> - <%= @issue_request.try(:issue_master).try(:name) %><br><br>

      <b>6. Support Group</b> - <%= @issue_request.try(:issue_tracker_group).try(:name) %><br><br>

      <b>7. Support Priority</b> - <%= @issue_request.try(:issue_priority) %><br><br>

      <b>8. Support Description</b> - <%= @issue_request.issue_master.try(:description) %><br><br>

      <b>9. Description</b> - <%= @issue_request.try(:description) %><br><br>
        With Regards,<br><br>
        
     </p>
  </body>
</html> 